                Webpush Domain wie im maximizly.app Kundenportal angeben. z.B. yourshop.de
            ]]></description>
            <description lang="en"><![CDATA[
                 Webpush Domain registered in the maximizly.app backend. e.g. yourshop.com
            ]]></description>
        </element>
    </elements>
</config>
